Class AbstractOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.AbstractOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Clause, PCExpression
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    And, Not

    public abstract class AbstractOperator
extends Object
implements Clause
    This class is the abstract class that gathers all the operator classes. It implements Clause.
    Author:
    Alexandre Camus

        public Clause getOperatorTail()
        Gets the tail of the operator. An operator is seen as its head (the first operand) and its tail (all the other operands).
        Returns:
        the tail of the operator as an object of the same class if there are several tail operands or as the operand itself if there is only one.
